         <abstract>
            <p>A general record for the Miracles of the Trinity, to be used when the exact collection cannot be identified.</p>
            <p>
               Several collections are transmitted under similar titles and contain prayers, homilies and miracles of the Trinity.
               Among these are:
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2281Trinity"/> (a collection of miracles of the Trinity attributed
               to <persName ref="PRS2748BeduaA"/>), 
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2282Trinity"/> (a collection of miracles of the 
               Trinity transmitted with <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1300Dersan"/>),
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2286ZenaSellase"/> (the collection <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2296Sayfas"/> (a collection of prayers to the Trinity arranged according
               to the days of the week) together with miracles of the Trinity).
            </p>

